{"tid":1549760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！有人唱香港國歌！","createTime":"2019-09-07T12:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T13:12:35.000Z","uid":2573,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b378d2dbf473be993f062f83c04307122a5f5ba7","tid":1549760,"uid":2573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:25:19.000Z","msg":"南區有手足搞咗個慶中秋活動<br />\n活動最後 手足帶大家唱願榮光歸香港<br />\n有人錄低咗 好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104566977589453/posts/113673326678818?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104566977589453%2Fposts%2F113673326678818%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=518fd4c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104566977589453/posts/113673326678818?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n南區呢個抗爭幼兒班真係要加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6218acebc97c5642566f7847008b5064adf42969","tid":1549760,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:25:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f139a49d10973f97087a41c004d27cce1318e7fe","tid":1549760,"uid":2573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:25:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da974aadfed2ab25204dbeeacaac23f5ca32d58","tid":1549760,"uid":149215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:26:20.000Z","msg":"背熟哂嘅舉手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41d9ed05d1b3fe4ea409b22a51b930806326e06","tid":1549760,"uid":26876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:26:52.000Z","msg":"借之前一個巴打寫嘅文一用<br />\n<br />\n佢哋大搖大擺行出警察宿舍，<br />\n每一個警察行過，都陰陰嘴笑鳩你班香港人：<br />\n「光復香港喎，時代革命喎。」<br />\n「曱甴。」<br />\n<br />\n每一個圍過警署嘅街坊，<br />\n都要接受依一班警察，<br />\n仲有佢哋家屬嘅冷眼。<br />\n「嗰隻甴曱啊，」佢指住你，<br />\n「嗰日佢咪圍鳩咗喺到囉，<br />\n依家咪死狗咁。」<br />\n<br />\n你忍唔住，你屌鳩佢老母。<br />\n不過佢一啲都無怕過你，<br />\n「甴曱！收皮啦！你打鳩我啊？！」<br />\n佢行埋嚟，再摸下你個頭，<br />\n「戇鳩仔。」<br />\n你忍住，你知道你唔可能打返佢。<br />\n佢拍拍你塊臉，<br />\n「點啊？你唔打鳩我喇？」<br />\n佢一啲收手嘅意欲都無，<br />\n因為警察已經為所欲為：<br />\n「又話黑警死全家？我全家仲喺到喎。」<br />\n<br />\n宿舍隔離就係警署，<br />\n警察一嚟到就會將你搭入去。<br />\n無人知道裏面會發生咩事。<br />\n你可能會畀人打一身、<br />\n畀人彈春袋、玩屎忽。<br />\n你女朋友喺你隔離，<br />\n你唔知道佢畀人拉埋入去之後會發生咩事，<br />\n你保護唔到你女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n「我要你同我道歉。」<br />\n警察一家望實你，同你講。<br />\n你唔敢再生事端。<br />\n「對唔住，好對唔住。」<br />\n最後你向警察道歉。<br />\n佢一邊拍你塊臉，一邊同你講，<br />\n「下次唔好喇。」<br />\n你覺得好興幸，<br />\n警察肯原諒你。<br />\n<br />\n依一個就係香港人放棄嘅結局，<br />\n你班「曱甴」依家想放棄未？"},{"pid":"56958bcfac79001a744c7b51daea839223c95833","tid":1549760,"uid":2573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:27:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南區九月九日和你拖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0AHZWbU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0AHZWbU.jpg&h=0696355d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/southernholdwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsouthernholdwithyou&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=6cab3947\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/southernholdwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"6849a92a50897964ced02c7bb16cf7ed8f4e143f","tid":1549760,"uid":2573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1da974aadfed2ab25204dbeeacaac23f5ca32d58","tid":1549760,"uid":149215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:26:20.000Z","msg":"背熟哂嘅舉手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:27:39.000Z","msg":"我願榮光歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6bc5fd6f3769368fcdefdcd73be3d4b0637a64","tid":1549760,"uid":2573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:27:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南區九月九日和你拖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0AHZWbU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0AHZWbU.jpg&h=0696355d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/southernholdwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsouthernholdwi